  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this prospective study is to see the natural course of adhesive capsulitis of
      hip. The study is based on the hypothesis that the natural course of adhesive capsulitis of
      hip is similar to that of adhesive capsulitis of shoulder. This study is also based on a
      hypothesis that hip joint capsule stretching exercise will result in pain relief, recovery of
      hip range of motion in months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
